TITLE: Victims trapped in Twin Towers on 9/11 sought help for themselves, others through phone calls
SUMMARY: Through the phone calls made by those inside the Twin Towers on 9/11, bravery, desperation and love for their friends and family outside can all be heard.

TITLE: Timeline of tragic events that occurred on Sept 11, 2001
SUMMARY: Sept. 11, 2001, was a day full of dread, chaos and horrific acts. Four hijacked planes took the lives of thousands. This timeline details the events that happened on the day.

TITLE: How Stairwell B became the site of a miracle amidst the tragedy of Sept. 11, 2001
SUMMARY: Fourteen survivors were protected from the north tower collapse in Stairwell B as the building fell around them. The story of their survival has become known as "the miracle of Stairwell B."
